# Regression Analysis

> [!INFO]
> used to describe the relationship between the dependent variable (y) and independent variable (x)

- independent variables (predictors, factors, treatment variables, explanatory variables, input variables, x-variables)
- dependent variables
	- what you want to use the model to explain or predict or the outcome
	- the outcome that you are studying
	- also known as the response variable, outcome variable, or y-variable
	- depends on the other x-variables
